    EventFilter

    public static final class EventFilter.Builder
extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<EventFilter.Builder>
implements EventFilterOrBuilder
     Filters `Event`s by:
   1. the type of the event message,
   2. aggregate ID,
   3. event message field values,
   4. values stored in `event_context` field of the event.
 The time of the event is filtered by `before` and `after` attributes of `EventStreamQuery`.
    Protobuf type spine.server.event.EventFilter
